long_description: Featherweight and very smooth, the Shimano Ultegra CS-6800 11-Speed Cassette makes lightning-quick shifts thanks to a rigid aluminum construction built with precise engineering. Choose among 11/25, 11/28 or 11/32 sprocket combinations; these gearing ratios provide combinations that work particularly well when combined with compact gearing. The Shimano Ultegra CS-6800 11-Speed Cassette features a nickel-plated finish.
